    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Ready for a reliable ride that won't let you down? This well-maintained vehicle is in good condition and has plenty of life left to give! The exterior presents nicely with only minor cosmetic blemishes from regular use \u2014 nothing that takes away from its solid, road-ready appearance. Under the hood, everything is running smoothly and dependably. If you're looking for a trustworthy everyday driver at a fair price, this one deserves a serious look!",
