    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 **Reliable & Ready to Go \u2014 Great Value for a Well-Maintained Vehicle!** If you're in the market for a dependable car that won't let you down, this is a fantastic choice! This car is in good condition \u2014 it's been well cared for and shows it. Expect a smooth, comfortable ride with no major issues to worry about. Some normal wear consistent with its age is present, but nothing that detracts from its solid performance and everyday reliability. Whether you're commuting, road-tripping, or just need a trustworthy daily driver, this one delivers real value at a fair price. Come take it for a spin \u2014 you won't be disappointed! \ud83d\ude4c",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly to reflect its true current condition \u2014 it is in poor shape and is best suited for a buyer who understands they are purchasing a project car or a basic transportation option with significant limitations. The car shows considerable wear both inside and out, with visible body damage, a worn interior, and mechanical issues that will require attention. It does run and can be driven, but reliability is not guaranteed and ongoing maintenance or repair costs should be expected. There are no luxury features or recent upgrades to speak of. This listing is priced accordingly to reflect the condition, and we encourage any interested buyer to inspect the vehicle thoroughly before purchasing. If you're a hands-on buyer, a mechanic, or simply need inexpensive transportation and are comfortable with the trade-offs, this could be a workable option at an honest price.",
      "price": 4500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Solid, Dependable & Ready to Go \u2014 A Genuinely Good Car at a Fair Price! This used car is in good condition, and we're proud to say it shows! It's been well-maintained, runs reliably, and presents nicely inside and out \u2014 not perfect, but genuinely solid and road-ready. You'll find normal wear consistent with its age, but nothing that detracts from its everyday dependability. If you're looking for a trustworthy vehicle that gives you real value without the new-car price tag, this one deserves a serious look. Come see it for yourself \u2014 we think you'll be pleasantly surprised!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good, solid condition \u2014 a dependable used car that has been conscientiously maintained and is ready for its next owner without requiring immediate repairs. The exterior presents well, showing only minor scuffs and light surface wear consistent with normal everyday use; there are no significant dents, rust, or structural concerns. The interior is clean and functional, with upholstery showing modest signs of use but nothing that detracts from comfort or daily drivability. Mechanically, the car runs reliably \u2014 the engine starts smoothly, the transmission shifts properly, and all major systems are in good working order. Brakes and tires have serviceable life remaining, though a buyer should budget for routine maintenance down the road as with any used vehicle. This is an honest, no-surprises car priced fairly for what it is \u2014 a solid choice for a buyer seeking reliable transportation without paying a premium for showroom-perfect condition.",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed at $35,000, a price that honestly reflects its solid good condition \u2014 and we're fully transparent about what that means. The exterior presents well overall: the paint retains a healthy shine with only minor surface blemishes, small door dings, or light scratches consistent with normal everyday use. There are no major dents or rust concerns, but it's not a showroom-perfect finish either. The interior is clean and comfortable, showing moderate wear on high-contact areas like the driver's seat and steering wheel, but nothing that detracts from daily enjoyment. Mechanically, the car runs reliably and confidently \u2014 the engine starts smoothly, transmission shifts cleanly, and all major systems are in good working order. You may find minor cosmetic imperfections here and there, but this is a genuinely dependable vehicle that has been reasonably cared for. It's the kind of car you can drive with confidence right off the lot, without the premium price tag of a mint-condition unit.",
      "price": 35000.0,
